Passwd::Keyring::Auto

Keyring makes it possible to securely preserve password in backends like
Gnome Keyring, KDE Wallet, OSX/Keychain etc.

While modules like Passwd::Keyring::Gnome handle specific backends, 
Passwd::Keyring::Auto tries to pick the best backend available.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Passwd::Keyring::Auto

You can also look for information at:

    http://bitbucket.org/Mekk/perl-keyring-auto

